Description: The Teamcity subdomain login page is vulnerable to CVE-2023-42793 which allows the creation of an admin user
Affected Users/Infra: This vulnerability affects all users of the Teamcity service on the standalone machine Gary.

Description: The SMB service on the standalone machine Windham is vulnerable to SambaCry which allows remote code execution
Affected Users/Infra: This vulnerability affects all users of the SMB service on the standalone machine Windham.
